            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Resolved rs11591147</strong> -&gt; resolver returned <code>['1:55039974:G:A']</code>; credible-set data is keyed under <code>1:55039974:G:T</code> (592 rows across resources/data types).</span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    },
