    {
      "id": "BYtC",
      "code_hash": "ff193bda65ecf735df93b0b8b4764154",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"to-extend\">To extend</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Swap <code>rs11591147</code> for <code>rs7412</code> (APOE, drives LDL via a different mechanism) and re-run \u2014\n  the dot plot should still be lipid-anchored but the QTL co-signals will look different.</li>\n<li>Take the top GWAS trait above and feed its <code>cs_id</code> into <code>/colocalization_by_credible_set_id/{id}</code>\n  to ask which other credible sets share this signal \u2014 that bridges PheWAS into the\n  colocalization view from nb01.</li>\n<li>Resolve the FinnGen phenocodes to human labels by calling\n  <code>/phenotype/finngen/{phenocode}/markdown</code> for each top trait, and re-render the y-axis\n  with readable names.</li>\n</ul></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
